1
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:56,320
They say marriage is

2
00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:58,120
the most important moment in a woman's life.

3
00:00:58,120 --> 00:01:01,840
Preparing for this day since birth.

4
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:02,800
Ma'am,

5
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,879
do you take the man beside you to be your husband?

6
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:05,600
I do.

7
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:08,880
I can't believe that someone like me with fear of intimacy

8
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:11,920
could have such a flawless wedding.

9
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:14,300
Everything is exactly as I imagined.

10
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,680
Wait.

11
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:20,840
Who is this?

12
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:21,920
This young man.

13
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:27,680
Come with me.

14
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:29,920
Oh my God.

15
00:01:30,039 --> 00:01:31,560
Is he taking me to elope?

16
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,120
This is too exciting!

17
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:35,080
Whatever.

18
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,460
I'll be brave for love just this once.

19
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,420
Mom, why are you so close to me?

20
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,360
Don't you have an exam

21
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,759
at 2:00 PM?

22
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:58,320
I'm doomed.

23
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,040
Look at you.

24
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:04,520
You can't wake up during the day and won't sleep at night.

25
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:06,780
How much more do I have to worry about you?

26
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,360
Mom, I'm already in college.

27
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:11,000
I know what I'm doing. You don't need to worry anymore.

28
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,760
I provide for your food, clothes, and tuition.

29
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:14,320
And I have to go to the hospital with you every day.

30
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:16,360
Now you get upset when I just say a few words?

31
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,920
The last thing my condition needs is care.

32
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,520
You already know that.

33
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,960
If you don't learn to take the initiative to get closer,

34
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,220
you're really doomed.

35
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,320
Mom, if you don't let me go,

36
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,420
my final exams will really be doomed.

37
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:29,600
I gotta go.

38
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,079
Bye, Mom.

39
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,840
I am Su Wan.

40
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:41,720
I have a severe fear of intimacy.

41
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:44,400
I am afraid of getting close to people.

42
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,000
Regardless of age or gender,

43
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:49,440
even my own mother can't get close to me.

44
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,480
But fortunately, animals are the exception.

45
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:01,400
So I chose a major

46
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,480
that my mom thinks

47
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:05,690
means unemployment after graduation: Animal Science.

48
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:08,240
In my own animal world,

49
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:11,320
I still live freely and happily.

50
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,280
Content.

51
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,400
Why is there a truck full of dogs?

52
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:42,880
Look at their blank eyes and hanging tongues.

53
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:44,600
They are obviously anxious and scared.

54
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,060
These must be stolen dogs.

55
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,000
Dog thieves.

56
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:51,320
Driver, please speed up

57
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,360
and catch up to that truck.

58
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:52,960
Sit tight.

59
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,920
Su Wan, where are you?

60
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:03,300
If you don't show up, we're going to fail.

61
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:15,080
Hello, professor.

62
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,640
This is our

63
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:17,640
final report on Animal Behavior Observation.

64
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,040
Our group members are...

65
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,080
Hello, what's up?

66
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:30,440
All groups have finished their reports.

67
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,040
Professor Liu said if you don't show up,

68
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,120
we'll both get zero for the final.

69
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,640
Okay, I got it.

70
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:35,890
I'll be right there.

71
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,520
Hello.

72
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,200
Tow truck.

73
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:04,620
No problem.

74
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:25,960
Young man.

75
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,040
You're here on a mission, right?

76
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:32,420
Don't worry, I know the rules.

77
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,240
I definitely won't tell anyone.

78
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,520
You must stay safe.

79
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,600
Don't be afraid, doggies.

80
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,560
I'm here to save you.

81
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,120
Good.

82
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,320
A little punishment for you.

83
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,780
Consider yourself lucky.

84
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,970
Don't be afraid.

85
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:10,900
Hurry up and go.

86
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,120
Be careful.

87
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,520
Come here.

88
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:23,800
Hurry.

89
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:26,040
Understood.

90
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,960
Don't worry.

91
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,530
I'll get it done right, bro.

92
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,760
Wait a moment, bro.

93
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,820
I'll hang up first.

94
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:41,180
Where's my dog?

95
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,000
Who let my dog out?

96
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,080
Who are you?

97
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:54,440
Hello.

98
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,400
You let them out, didn't you?

99
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,000
What's going on?

100
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,960
Don't smile at me.

101
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:06,000
Why are you doing this when you are so young?

102
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,860
Why did you let people's dogs out?

103
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,480
My eyes!

104
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,440
Dog thieves, we will never meet again.

105
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,160
Bye-bye.

106
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,880
Just you wait.

107
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,240
You little brat.

108
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,400
If I catch you,

109
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,730
I'll skin you alive.

110
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,480
I'm really out of luck today.

111
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,440
My dog is gone,

112
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,960
and I lost my keys.

113
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:43,880
No big deal.

114
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,520
Come pick it up in three days.

115
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,920
Su Wan.

116
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,440
You just wait.

117
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,000
Su Wan.

118
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,640
Probably not the same person.

119
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,500
Do you know her?

120
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:00,800
Where are you going?

121
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,120
I'm going to get revenge.

122
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:04,040
I'll leave the car to you. Thanks.

123
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,680
Hello, Professor Liu.

124
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,880
There's nothing to say.

125
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:13,000
I've already submitted a zero for your group.

126
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,760
Normally, during experiments,

127
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:16,420
you never cooperate well with your classmates.

128
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,760
Now you even dare to miss the final exam.

129
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,560
If you do this again next semester,

130
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,560
just drop out.

131
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,130
No, Professor Liu, I...

132
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,640
Professor Liu, it really is my fault this time.

133
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,840
Please give Ding Shiyu another chance,

134
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,679
okay?

135
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,440
What do you want to do?

136
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,120
What do you think I want to do?

137
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,160
Don't come over.

138
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:55,120
I'll call the police if you come any closer.

139
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,880
Call them.

140
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,920
Let the police tell you

141
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:00,320
how many years you'll get for theft.

142
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,800
I'm telling you, I'm sick.

143
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,440
If you come over, you'll be in mortal danger.

144
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,520
I'm not kidding.

145
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,040
I want revenge.

146
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,680
Are you crazy? I...

147
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,440
It's not right to hit a woman.

148
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,570
I give up. Stop fighting, okay?

149
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,040
Let's get out of here.

150
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,720
We shouldn't stay here for long.
